data.description: PRICE ADJUSTMENT! COUNTRY LIVING JUST MINUTES AWAY FROM COLLIERVILLE AND OLIVE BRANCH!  Come see this meticulous kept home that is Located close to I269 and convenient to Olive Branch! Open floor plan that is complete with vaulted ceilings and arched doorways!! Updated lighting and plumbing fixtures throughout, freshly painted interior and exterior! Enjoy the large great room with gas fireplace and hardwood flooring! This home has a dining room that leads into the kitchen, perfect for entertaining!! The kitchen has an eat-in area, stainless-steel appliances and tile flooring. There is an extra roomy primary bedroom, bathroom that includes a jetted tub, separate shower and double vanities. This home is a split plan with two bedrooms and hall bath on the opposite side of the primary. Also, there is a 4th bedroom/bonus room upstairs.  A HUGE BACKYARD AND DECK with wood fence!  Roof is 3 years old! This is a must see!!
